{"tid":1567433,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"森美：政治就係一個三個人就會產生嘅野","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:05:48.000Z","uid":115866,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"edab6af632ba142fa308658587d696b6510a3817","tid":1567433,"uid":115866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsSxjZa94-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsSxjZa94-8&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=74a410d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsSxjZa94-8</a><br />\n5:58 <br />\n杜生：你覺得藝人應否就政治議題表態？<br />\n森美：應該可以表態啦。政治意思係咩呢？政治就係一個三個人就會產生嘅野。如果我同你兩個（指向杜生），究竟著長褲定短褲好？無野好講，你鐘意短，我鐘意長，無意思架。有第三個人就唔同啦（指向Fatson)，我地可以問佢，你覺得著長定短好？政治就係究竟嗰一個人，企去邊邊。<br />\n<br />\n森美大哥今集尾透露自己好似生cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3ebefa171bed8f6818ae2079e48fd1d010d1c3","tid":1567433,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6v9Jdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6v9Jdp.jpg&h=6cbe719f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFtYML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFtYML.jpg&h=a79b44b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d479b2f53f81fee20440c8114fb343ac27517515","tid":1567433,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"森美係香港人的英雄"},{"pid":"36b0ed105763a3b8947c836347dc97d2d29f38e0","tid":1567433,"uid":300718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"唔好等到十一，入黎打長期戰。<br />\n<br />\n【新主線：民間遞進民主平台】<br />\n<br />\n盡用人數優勢，以民主爭取民主，打長期戰。邀請有心巴絲加入策劃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566855<